name: End Point Corporation
tag_list: internet, ecommerce, scalability, security, postgresql, ruby-on-rails, perl, django
overview:
End Point Corporation develops, maintains, and hosts ecommerce and other database-driven Internet solutions for clients in many industries.

Our headquarters is in New York City, and our employees are located throughout the United States. We are passionate about open source and actively contribute to projects including PostgreSQL, Interchange, Spree, Bucardo, and Puppet.

We are experienced with all layers of the Internet technology stack: creating engaging customer-facing web interfaces, optimizing search and site performance, developing scalable server applications, designing and tuning databases, and automating and monitoring cloud and traditional systems deployments.
